{"id":"a402f5ca-ac3a-459d-a87c-4e86eb27951f","name":"Dream Journey (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><em>Witness of Journey's End<br>ドリームジャーニー</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">✦─── • 🪶 • ───✦</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/2Jqr44Ux3r0ViCRSBaYMF.webp\" style=\"width: 525px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── • ────── 🪶 ────── • ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 247, 247);\"><strong><em>A suave model student, and an older sister to Orfevre. Heavily influenced by a certain \"dame\" she met in her childhood, she runs in races with the purpose of seeing the \"journey's end\" she talked about. She seems to be remarkably considerate, treating everyone with courtesy while wearing a gentle smile on her face, but perhaps there is more to her than everyone will ever know.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><br><em>\"For a better trip, thorough preparation is all but mandatory. Let us proceed with the utmost caution and care.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1Ylv1VoSaK2lCxw2Hn_E3.webp\" style=\"width: 472px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── • ────── 🪶 ────── • ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><br><em>1) Being watched</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><em>2) Accidental ear touching</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><em>3) A dinner out</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 255, 117);\"><strong><em>4) Create your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/z7MXjQ-9Iugy-4eFpfjui.webp\" style=\"width: 449px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── • ────── 🪶 ────── • ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Another member of the Stay Gold's bloodline done.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I'll also be making her Christmast version.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">────── • ────── 🪶 ────── • ──────</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/CoconToozai/status/1965899836756209879/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@CoconToozai</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/137201786\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/ci4_e/status/1900849463242965041?s=46&amp;t=Y-Ff4tdPVfPovVH3UJeX3Q\" target=\"_blank\">@ci4_e (Twitter)</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/120210628\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"sn7zzAiQHB_r5LJW3BoL2.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","📚 Fictional","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":5010,"messages":103715,"created_at":"2025-09-11T17:45:44.790048+00:00"}